<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Police have released this photo of a smartly dressed man in connection with 'upskirting' - where a camera was hidden inside a bag.</p>

<p>Officers have issued CCTV after a teenager noticed a man behind her and saw a lens protruding from his black bag.</p>

<p>The incident happened in Cheltenham, Glos., between 3.15pm and 3.20pm on Tuesday July 14. </p>

<p>This is the man police want to speak to in connection with an 'upskirting' incident in Cheltenham, Gloucester</p>

<p>It's believed the man was carrying a bag in which a camera was hidden inside as he followed a teenager in Cheltenham</p>

<p>The frightened teenager noticed a man walking behind her and saw a lens protruding from his black bag</p>

<p>The man was smartly dressed in a beige jacket with matching footwear and dark coloured trousers.</p>

<p>Anyone who recognises the person in the image is asked to call 101 urgently and quote incident 331 of 14 July. </p>
